{"article_id":"95BZ1gkVL8eSl3us","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON ( ) -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"President Donald Trump ' s planned \" great , great wall \" began morphing into a physical barrier and an array of high-tech gadgets in congressional talks","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"launched on Wednesday","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"to forge a compromise on security at the U.S. border with Mexico .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"Although there were no guarantees","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"a deal could be reached by a Feb. 15 deadline ,","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"lawmakers on both sides showed a willingness","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"to avoid ultimatums and seek common ground .","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"Some negotiators from Trump ' s Republican Party avoided uttering the word \" wall \" during the 17-member border security panel ' s first session on Wednesday .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"They spoke of a mix of enforcement tools ,","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"as Democrats had urged .","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"The long , contentious debate over one of Trump ' s biggest 2016 campaign promises","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"- a concrete border wall","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"financed by Mexico -","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"entered a new stage","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"with the committee ' s launch last week","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"ending a 35-day partial closure of the government .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"Lawmakers have an opportunity ,","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"Republican Senator Shelley Moore Capito said ,","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"to choose \" all of the above \" for border investments ,","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"\" including physical barriers","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"where it makes sense . \"","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"Even Trump ' s early-morning Twitter message on the committee ' s urgent work left some wiggle room on the wall .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"\" If the committee of Republicans and Democrats","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"now meeting on Border Security","depth":12},{"id":25,"text":"is not discussing or contemplating a Wall or Physical Barrier ,","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"they are Wasting their time ! \"","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"he tweeted .","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"The Feb. 15 deadline was imposed","depth":5},{"id":29,"text":"when Trump agreed last week to end the shutdown","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"and give lawmakers another chance","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"to forge a deal","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"or face another closure .","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"At a news conference , Democrats handed out a fact sheet","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"they described as their opening proposal .","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"It included no money for a wall or physical barriers ,","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"but House Appropriations Committee Chairwoman Nita Lowey said :","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"\" Everything ' s on the table . \"","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"But she added :","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"\" Smart border security is not overly reliant on physical barriers ,","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"which","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"the Trump administration has failed to demonstrate","depth":13},{"id":42,"text":"are cost effective","depth":13},{"id":43,"text":"compared to better technology and more personnel ... \"","depth":13},{"id":44,"text":"Every dollar","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"spent on ineffective proposals","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"means one less dollar","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"invested in measures","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"that actually keep us safe . \"","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"Instead of Trump ' s wall , Democrats have been urging investment in high-tech equipment","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"to enhance border security , such as drones , sensors and advanced scanning equipment , along with additional law enforcement personnel .","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"On Dec. 22 , about a quarter of the U.S. government closed ,","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"leaving 800,000 federal workers without pay for the next five weeks .","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"The shutdown was prompted by Trump ' s demand","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"that any shutdown-ending legislation contain $ 5.7 billion for his wall .","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"Mexico long ago refused to pay for it .","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"Trump now wants U.S. taxpayers to foot the bill for a project","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"that","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"some estimates have shown","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"could cost more than $ 23 billion .","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"He says","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"it is needed","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"to keep out undocumented immigrants and illegal drugs .","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"Democrats broadly support more border security ,","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"but oppose the wall","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"and stood firm against Trump ' s demand","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"that money for it be part of shutdown-ending legislation .","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"Trump temporarily gave up that demand on Friday","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"and agreed to the committee .","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"Congress has until Feb. 15 to pass a package","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"to fund several federal agencies","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"through Sept. 30 .","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"That gives lawmakers little more than a week","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"to settle their differences","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"and leave time","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"for both houses of Congress","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"to debate","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"and vote on any deal .","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"Trump has moved off his demand for a 2,000-mile","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"( 3,219 km )","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"concrete barrier","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"and now talks about either a wall or \" physical barrier \" on only some parts of the border .","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"Democrats in the past have backed \" fencing . \"","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"The Department of Homeland Security says","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"654 miles of pedestrian and vehicle barriers already exist .","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"Democrats repeatedly have voted for $ 1.3 billion in added border funds for this year .","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"Late last year , Trump even signaled his willingness to go along with that figure","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"before reversing course","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"and insisting on $ 5.7 billion for his wall .","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"The personalized gavel of House Appropriations Committee Chairwoman Nita Lowey","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"( D-NY ) ,","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"serving as the Chairwoman of a bipartisan group of U.S. lawmakers from both the U.S. Senate and U.S. House of Representatives ,","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"is seen at the start of their first public negotiating session over the U.S. federal government shutdown and border security on Capitol Hill in Washington , U.S.","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"January 30 , 2019 .","depth":6},{"id":94,"text":"/Yuri Gripas","depth":5},{"id":95,"text":"Wednesday ' s committee meeting might be the only public session ,","depth":5},{"id":96,"text":"with future sessions likely behind closed doors .","depth":5},{"id":97,"text":"If lawmakers do not craft a deal","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"Trump likes ,","depth":7},{"id":99,"text":"he has threatened two possible next steps :","depth":7},{"id":100,"text":"another shutdown ,","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"or declaring a \" national emergency \"","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"and taking existing funds","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"appropriated by Congress for other purposes","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"- possibly from the Defense Department , for example -","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"to build his wall .","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"There is bipartisan opposition in Congress to the emergency strategy ,","depth":6},{"id":107,"text":"which likely would spark a legal challenge .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":215,"left":0,"right":214,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":214,"left":157,"right":213,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":157,"left":134,"right":156,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":134,"left":110,"right":133,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":110,"left":1,"right":109,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":109,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":133,"left":116,"right":132,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":116,"left":113,"right":115,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":113,"left":111,"right":112,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":111,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":112,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":115,"left":8,"right":114,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":114,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"left":121,"right":131,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":121,"left":119,"right":120,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":119,"left":118,"right":14,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":118,"left":11,"right":117,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":117,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":120,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":131,"left":125,"right":130,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":122,"right":124,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":19,"right":123,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":20,"right":21,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"par